snippet.title: Ludical Update Trailer #2 (itch.io)
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! Guess what? The demo is finally out now! Can you believe it? Anyway, that was the update lol! Also, the full game release is coming sometime this June so keep your eyes open and ready to start gaming :D

https://newbo-games.itch.io/ludical
